  <body class="- topic/body " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/wn_positron_5.dita" xtrc="body:1;11:9">
    <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/wn_positron_5.dita" xtrc="p:1;12:8">The new <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/wn_positron_5.dita" xtrc="b:2;12:19">Oxygen AI Positron Assistant 5.0</b> brings meaningful improvements to help
      content creators use AI more effectively in structured authoring.</p>
    <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/wn_positron_5.dita" xtrc="p:2;14:8">One of the most useful updates is the ability to <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/wn_positron_5.dita" xtrc="b:3;14:60">generate or update files</b> like
        <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/wn_positron_5.dita" xtrc="b:4;15:12">XSLT</b>, <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/wn_positron_5.dita" xtrc="b:5;15:25">XSD</b>, <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/wn_positron_5.dita" xtrc="b:6;15:37">Schematron</b>, <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/wn_positron_5.dita" xtrc="b:7;15:56">JSON Schema</b>, and <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/wn_positron_5.dita" xtrc="b:8;15:80">DTD</b> just by
      providing a brief description. You can then review changes using the built-in <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/wn_positron_5.dita" xtrc="b:9;16:88">visual file
        comparison</b> tool.</p>
    <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/wn_positron_5.dita" xtrc="p:3;18:8">For <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/wn_positron_5.dita" xtrc="b:10;18:15">DITA users</b>, the assistant now supports advanced <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/wn_positron_5.dita" xtrc="b:11;18:70">content transformation</b>,
      making it easy to convert between document types or restructure topics using AI
      suggestions.</p>
    <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/wn_positron_5.dita" xtrc="p:4;21:8">Other key updates include:</p>
    <ul id="ul_i11_wlq_mfc" class="- topic/ul " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/wn_positron_5.dita" xtrc="ul:1;22:29">
      <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/wn_positron_5.dita" xtrc="li:1;23:11">
