      </li>
      <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/wn_positron_5.dita" xtrc="li:2;26:11">
        <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/wn_positron_5.dita" xtrc="p:6;27:12">The option to <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/wn_positron_5.dita" xtrc="b:13;27:29">exclude specific files</b> from AI processing</p>
      </li>
      <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/wn_positron_5.dita" xtrc="li:3;29:11">
        <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/wn_positron_5.dita" xtrc="p:7;30:12"><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/wn_positron_5.dita" xtrc="b:14;30:15">Callback functions</b> for validation or tool integration</p>
      </li>
      <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/wn_positron_5.dita" xtrc="li:4;32:11">
        <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/wn_positron_5.dita" xtrc="p:8;33:12">Support for attaching <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/wn_positron_5.dita" xtrc="b:15;33:37">Word, PowerPoint, and PDF</b> files as input</p>
      </li>
      <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/wn_positron_5.dita" xtrc="li:5;35:11">
        <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/wn_positron_5.dita" xtrc="p:9;36:12">Access to new reasoning models like <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/wn_positron_5.dita" xtrc="b:16;36:51">o3</b>, <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/wn_positron_5.dita" xtrc="b:17;36:62">o1</b>, <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/wn_positron_5.dita" xtrc="b:18;36:73">o4-mini</b>, and more</p>
      </li>
      <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/wn_positron_5.dita" xtrc="li:6;38:11">
        <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/wn_positron_5.dita" xtrc="p:10;39:12">Integration with <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/wn_positron_5.dita" xtrc="b:19;39:32">xAI Grok</b> and other custom AI services through specialized
          connectors</p>
      </li>
